metadata.description:
dream story 3
A chair given by heavenly fairies.
It is colorful, decorated, and radiant.
I got the impression that this was a king's chair.
I sit in the chair of the Heavenly King and enjoy the splendid dance of the fairies.
The dream story of Consteller D.L., who shines in the King's Chair. Series 3.
